Class ArrayList<E>

  • java.lang.Object
    • ArrayList<E>

  • public class ArrayList<E>
extends java.lang.Object
    Array basedimplementation of a list data structure.

    Performs dynamic resizing of itself upon adding of any new elements when size does not have necessary capacity.
